<h2>Format</h2>
<p>10 digits: the first 6 are the date of birth (YYMMDD), the next 3 encode area and birth order (ninth digit even for boy, odd for girl), and the tenth is a check digit.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unique_citizenship_number">Uniform Civil Number</a>.</p>
